Package org.apache.struts.chain.commands.generic

Contains generic commands.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
CopyFormToContext Subclass this command and configure it as part of a per-forward chain to perform any necessary pre-population or other preparation for a form before control is dispatched to the view layer.
WrappingLookupCommand Variant on chain LookupCommand which can optionally wrap the context it passes to the looked up command in an alternative class.
